<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PersonNote/24> rdfs:label "Person Note: #24" ;
	a dprr:PersonNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "On the cognomen, see Cic. Phil. 5.5 and 7, Cotylo, but in Phil. 8.24 and 28, and 13.26, Cotyla. In Plut. Ant. 18.8, it is #; cf. Cotulo in CIL 12.5686. On the praenomen, see Cic. Phil. 8.33. See MRR 2.323.\n" .
